snippet.title: Unholy Console Reveal Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Prepare yourself for the ultimate horror experience in Unholy! Coming to next-gen consoles on September 13th, 2024, this dark and twisted world will take you to the brink of fear. Journey through eerie landscapes as you uncover the secrets of a mysterious cult, all while facing terrifying foes who will stop at nothing to destroy you. Will you survive the darkness, or will you become its latest victim?

Watch the official Unholy Console Reveal Date Trailer now, and get ready to immerse yourself in a horrifying battle for survival when Unholy launches on Xbox Series X|S and PlayStation 5.

Mark your calendars—Friday the 13th is about to get a whole lot scarier.
